### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:9090
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Login to get JWT token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### 2. Get all teams (to get a team ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teams
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

> {%
    client.global.set("team_id", response.body[0].id);
%}

### 3. Create a new project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "teamId": "{{team_id}}",
  "name": "Mobile App Redesign",
  "description": "Complete overhaul of the mobile application UI/UX"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("project_id", response.body.id);
%}

### 4. Get project by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 5. Get all projects for a team
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/team/{{team_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 6. Update project
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{project_id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "name": "Mobile App Redesign - Phase 2",
  "description": "Updated scope: focusing on Android first"
}

### 7. Create another project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "teamId": "{{team_id}}",
  "name": "Backend API Refactor",
  "description": "Migrate legacy endpoints to new architecture"
}

### 8. Get all projects again (should see both)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/team/{{team_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 9. Delete project (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 10. Verify deleted project is not returned
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/team/{{team_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 11. Test - Try to access non-existent project
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 12. Test - Missing authorization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{project_id}}